'''Pho Ph'eahese''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Pho Ph'eahian]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Pho Ph'eah/Legends|Pho Ph'eah]]. The language was composed of squeaks, squeals and high-pitched barks. Its written form used an intricate set of characters to create a syllabary. Most Pho Ph'eahian were fluent in both Pho Ph'eahese and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], being literate in both languages.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

